title: Kim Kardashian Posts Intimate Photos of Her Engagement to Kanye West
text:
Kim Kardashian Posts Intimate Photos of Her Engagement to Kanye West Posted today at 11:30am 
Peter Kramer/NBC (LOS ANGELES) -- To celebrate getting engaged to Kanye West two years ago, Kim Kardashian posted Thursday a bunch of intimate photos from the couple's big day at San Francisco's AT&T Park. 
"#TBT to 2 years ago when I got engaged!" the reality star wrote on Instagram next to a photo of her kissing her now husband. A sign saying, "Pleeese Marry Meee!!!" lit up the photo's background. 
A photo posted by Kim Kardashian West (@kimkardashian) on Oct 22, 2015 at 3:48pm PDT 
Along with showing fans a close up of her engagement ring, Kardashian shared: "I was blind folded, with an orchestra playing & I had no idea what was about to happen!!!" 
Oct 22, 2015 at 4:29pm PDT 
She added that it was the "best surprise ever!"
